title: Romain Grosjean Accident.
notes: Romain Grosjean collided with the Armco barrier in the Grand Prix and the front half chassis of the vehicle exploded into a fireball. Remarkably Grosjean was able to emerge from the wreck without major injuries after having encountered a terrifying accident.

title: Max Verstappen Wins Abu Dhabi Grand Prix
notes: Max Verstappen takes pole position for the final race of the season. Verstappen ended with a final time of 1:27:45 and earned 25 points for Red Bull Racing. Charles Leclerc of Ferrari and Sergio Perez of Red Bull Racing also managed to earn a podium spot achieving 2nd and 3rd place respectively.

title: Sergio Perez Wins 2022 Monaco GP
notes: Sergio Perez was able to secure first place at the 2022 Monaco Grand Prix. Carlos Seinz and Max Verstappen earned was able to podium at 2nd and 3rd place respectively. The race had Charles Leclerc starting in pole position with Lando Norris achieving the fastest lap time of 1:14.693.

title: My Friends first F1 Grand Prix
notes: My friend attended his first Formula 1 Grand Prix and we had an amazing time! I got to see my favorite driver Max Verstappen secure the first place win which made my whole trip.

title: Mick Schumacher crashes at Japan GP
notes: The weather was wet and rainy at the Japanese Grand Prix, which Mick Schumacher blamed for his crash. He stated that the spray hampered his visibility which resulted into the big crash he endured.

title: George Russel earns 1st in Brazil
circuit: Autódromo José Carlos Pace in Interlagos
notes: George Russell was able to clinch first place during the Brazilian Grand Prix. He finished with a time of 1:38:34.044 with Lewis Hamilton and Carlos Seinz finishing in 2nd and 3rd.

title: Lewis Hamilton experienced big crash at Belgian GP
notes: Hamilton suffered a 45G impact after collision with Fernando Alonso. Fortunately Hamilton stated that he was okay after the accident. The two were former teammates which adds to the drama of the whole situation.
